snippet.title: Car Races #1 - VC4000
snippet.description: With 5 different game styles and 1 or 2 player modes this game has hours of Entertainment. This game was also copied to other early game consoles like the Videopac console. The controls are a bit jumpy on my console. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2013/11/car-races-1-vc-4000.html
